        "title": "fix: show official owner badges across public surfaces",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Preserve computed `owner.official` on skill detail owner responses, including the reported `steipete` member-owned skill page.\n- Preserve computed `owner.official` on public skill list entries so `/skills?sort=downloads`, related lists, trending lists, highlighted lists, and audit list rows can render owner-official badges.\n- Preserve `owner.official` through package detail queries and the `/api/v1/packages/:name` response schema.\n- Render compact Official badges from either the skill's own official badge or the computed official owner flag.\n\n## Validation\n- `bun run test convex/lib/officialPublishers.test.ts convex/skills.publicListCursor.test.ts src/components/SkillListItem.test.tsx`\n- `bun run test convex/skills.public.test.ts`\n- `bun run test convex/packages.public.test.ts`\n- `bun run test src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx`\n- `bun run test convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts packages/schema/src/schemas.test.ts`\n- `bun run format:check`\n- `bun run lint`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx tsc --noEmit`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/schema/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/clawhub/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bunx convex dev --once`\n\n## Local UI Check\nPatched dev Convex was seeded with the exact reported routes, then checked locally at `390x844`, `768x1024`, and `1440x900`:\n\n| Route | Result |\n| --- | --- |\n| `/steipete/codex-owner-move-debug-1778257045` | title Official tag present; owner compact Official badge present; no horizontal overflow |\n| `/plugins/@openclaw/whatsapp` | title Official tag present; owner compact Official badge present; no horizontal overflow |\n| `/skills?sort=downloads` | `Codex Owner Move Debug` now has one compact Official badge from `owner.official`, even though `skill.badges` is empty |\n\nThe local Playwright check reported no console errors after ignoring the existing dev-only theme hydration warning.\n",
